  <brief_title>Radiotherapy With or Without Concurrent Chemotherapy for Extensive Lymphatic Metastasis of Esophageal Cancer - 3JECROG-P03</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase III Study of Simultaneous Integrated Boost Intensity Modulated Radiation Therapy (SIB-IMRT) With or Without Concurrent Chemotherapy Followed by Consolidation Chemotherapy for Extensive Lymphatic Metastasis of Esophageal Cancer - 3JECROG-P03</official_title>
