  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aimed to compare elective nodal irradiation versus involved field
      irradiation with or without concurrent chemotherapy and the addition of consolidation
      chemotherapy for patients with extensive lymphatic metastasis of esophageal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
